evaluate

EvaluationReport evaluate(java.util.List<java.lang.Boolean> predictions,
                          ExampleSet examples)
                          throws java.lang.IllegalArgumentException
Evaluates the performance of the model over the given labeled examples. The model features must match the example features.

Parameters:
predictions - The predictions to evaluate.
examples - The examples to use for evaluation.
Returns:
The EvaluationReport.
Throws:
java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - If the model features do not match the examples features.
